org.sakaiproject.calendar.impl

Class RecurrenceRuleBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.calendar.impl.RecurrenceRuleBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecurrenceRule
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DailyRecurrenceRule, MonthlyRecurrenceRule, MWFRecurrenceRule, TThRecurrenceRule, WeeklyRecurrenceRule, YearlyRecurrenceRule

    public abstract class RecurrenceRuleBase
extends Object
implements RecurrenceRule
    This is a common base for the daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly recurrence rules.
